Items.text: You did it! My cart is unstuck!
Items.name: Ms Sparks

Items.text: Oh, thank you both so much!
Items.name: Ms Sparks

Items.text: Here, let me get you something from the cart.
Items.name: Ms Sparks

Items.text: I usually sell these for $5 a pop to unsuspecting tourists!
Items.name: Ms Sparks

Items.text: Well, I've got to get going.
Items.name: Ms Sparks

Items.text: I sell various odds and ends, so keep an eye out for me around town.
Items.name: Ms Sparks
